This is to certify that Mr. Peter Fenjves, born February 6,1920, was awarded the doctoral
degree of Technical Sciences (Dr.sc.techn.) on February 1, 1946, based on his thesis work
and the oral examination. There is no grading system for doctoral exams, (pass or fail).
The Swiss Federal Institute of Technology Zürich offers no transcripts in connection with its
Doctoral Program because this curriculum starts at a level which is equivalent with the
Ph.D. qualifying examination of the American university system. Therefore there is no
formal course requirement.
